  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "US delegation meets President",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "US Deputy Treasurer for Asia Robert Caproth, Deputy Assistant Secretary of State for South and Central Asia Kelly Kiederlin, US Ambassador to Sri Lanka Julie Chung and President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa met today (27).",
        "It is said that the current economic crisis in Sri Lanka was discussed at the meeting.",
        "The delegation stated that it would forge a long-term partnership to assist Sri Lanka in building a prosperous, secure and democratic future, and that the United States would continue to support Sri Lanka during these difficult times."
      ],
